data.description:
Feel right at home in this 4 bedroom 3 full baths 1.5 story home! This beautiful established neighborhood is close to shopping and yet is off the beaten path. Stainless kitchen appliances stay and the roof, flooring and two  HVAC systems are only 5 years old! Main bedroom and ensuite are downstairs and 3 bedrooms and one full bath are upstairs. there is another full bath downstairs as well. The open floor plan is spacious and has a vaulted ceiling and skylights that give it grandeur!
The back yard has a deck and patio and is flat and fenced. This home is stylish, comfortable and roomy! A must see!
